      "writtenOn": "2018-10-12T20:05:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "you can have a go enum based on string. \n\n  type CollapsingPreference string\n\n  const (\n    Collapsed CollapsingPreference \u003d \"collapsed\"\n    Expanded CollapsingPreference  \u003d \"expanded\"\n    NonGreen CollapsingPreference \u003d \"non-green\"\n  )\n\nthis is how other Go code is written in cases like this, so I think this code should follow that too",
      "parentUuid": "f477ef0b_bad9ed85",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 62,
        "startChar": 31,
        "endLine": 62,
        "endChar": 77
      },
